Build Instructions
==================

Environment:
- OS: Windows 10 21H2
- Node.js version: 22.16.0
- npm version: 10.9.2

Build Instructions:
- Open a terminal and go to the ext_installer directory.
- Run: npm install
- Then run: npm run build

The build script will create a file named ext_installer.zip inside the dist/firefox/ folder.
This zip contains the extension with all JavaScript files bundled and minified.
Source maps are included alongside the .js and .css files.

Notes:
- The build process uses esbuild to bundle and minify the code.
- Tested with the environment listed above.
- No additional setup is required.
